## Token System

Il compilatore uses **~80 keyword tokens**. Each token corresponds to exactly one keyword (English).

Le keyword table now has **80 entries** (down from 160).
Il Less maintenance burden
    One file instead of two
    Reduced documentation size by ~50%
    
